description: Enterprise techniques used by PsExec, ATT&CK software S0029 v1.0
name: PsExec (S0029)

techniques.comment: Microsoft Sysinternals PsExec is a popular administration tool that can be used to execute binaries on remote systems using a temporary Windows service.
PsExec, a tool that has been used by adversaries, writes programs to the ADMIN$ network share to execute commands on remote systems.
